name: com.famobi.game-interface
description:
Plugin to easily integrate GameInterface API into Unity projects.

CRITICAL: Before starting integration, you MUST read the official Game Interface documentation at https://docs.famobi.com/

IMPORTANT: Please also read the README.md file before starting integration.

Official Documentation: https://docs.famobi.com/

Check out Packages/Game Interface/Samples for a test scene, where features can be tested.
Note: To open the sample scene, you must copy it to your Assets/ folder first (scenes in Packages folder cannot be opened directly).
Also check out the GameInterfaceExample.cs script to see example usage.
